1. Introduction
------------------------

Welcome to Acpi,a quick tool for recuperate information about battery,temperature,etc...

2. Prerequisites
------------------------

Acpi requires that your kernel is configured with acpi.

3. Installation
________________________

Do this, in the following order:

        perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make install

